snippet: A program encompassing works by Dvorak, Brahms and Franck was performed at a lunchtime chamber-music concert on Thursday at the 92nd Street Y.
abstract: Corinna da Fonseca-Wollheim reviews chamber-music performance by violinist Jaime Laredo at 92nd Street Y.
